      <title>How to Lose Weight Quick with No More Fad Diets</title>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;How to Lose Weight Fast Safely - No More Fad Diets!&lt;br&gt;By &lt;a href="http://ezinearticles.com/?expert=Allison_R"&gt;Allison R&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I'm sure you know that some diets and diet pills are dangerous. Do you want to find out how to lose weight fast safely? There is a plan that teaches you the steps of quick weight loss, and it is a very safe and healthy plan. If you are interested in a plan that helps you drop the pounds without starvation or calorie counting, keep reading!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Most people know that diet pills can be dangerous and have even caused death in some cases. Fad diets aren't healthy and can leave you depleted of vitamins and minerals, which can cause many health problems. In this article I will show you how to lose weight fast and do it safely.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By eating a balanced diet that contains proteins, carbs and fats (yes, you can eat fats and still lose weight), you can train your body to burn calories fast. If you are one of the people who eat mostly processed foods and fast foods, try adding some of the foods below to increase metabolism. This will help you lose weight.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;How to Lose Weight Fast Safely&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here are foods that should be added to your diet: Fresh fruits and vegetables, dairy products, beans, whole grain cereals and breads, nuts and seeds. Also, spicy foods are good for fast weight loss because many contain cayenne pepper and garlic, which are great fat burning foods.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Drinking your share of water and green tea will also help to increase metabolism, which will help your body burn fat and calories. Drink 6 or 8 glasses of water every day, and 1 or 2 glasses of green tea. Beware though, most green tea contains some caffeine so drink it earlier in the day to avoid sleep problems.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Eat more often. Instead of eating three large meals, try eating 4 or 5 smaller meals throughout the day. Not only does this increase metabolism, it also cuts down on hunger between meals. This means less snacking.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How to lose weight fast safely? Follow the tips above and add in a little exercise. This doesn't have to be a chore. Simply doing some weight bearing exercise for 15 or 20 minutes three times per week will cause your body to burn fat for much longer than other exercise.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is an online diet plan that teaches you all the steps of a method called "calorie switching". This plan shows you how and what to eat, and how you can lose weight fast without ever counting a calorie, fat gram or carb. It has helped thousands of people with quick weight loss, and many lose 15 pounds in less than one month - without risking their health!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in learning how to lose weight fast safely, I suggest you take a look at this popular program. At a cost that is far less than the price of a weeks worth of diet foods on other programs, it is well worth your investment!&lt;/p&gt;


